---

## 🧪 Jenkinsfile

pipeline {
    agent any

    stages {
        stage('Checkout') {
            steps {
                git 'your-repo-url'
            }
        }

        stage('Build') {
            steps {
                sh 'docker build -t your-image .'
            }
        }

        stage('Sonar') {
            steps {
                sh 'sonar-scanner'
            }
        }

        stage('Push') {
            steps {
                sh 'docker push your-image'
            }
        }

        stage('Deploy') {
            steps {
                sh 'ansible-playbook -i inventory playbook.yml'
            }
        }
    }
}

---

## 🔐 Best Practices

- Use SSH keys  
- Store secrets in Jenkins credentials  
- Use version tags for Docker images  
- Enforce Sonar quality gates  

---

## 💡 Summary

Automated pipeline from code → test → quality → Docker → deploy → live app

